      "description": "List Habits, is a lightweight, minimalist punch card, record life, develop good habits software.\n\nRead books, memorize words, study for exams, take exams, get certified, exercise, lose weight, work out, gain muscle, go to bed early, wake up early, keep accounts, save money and other life points, insist on daily punching, develop good habits and record your growth every step of the way.\n\nFeatures:\n- Support the creation of an unlimited number of habits.\n- Using different colors and icons to distinguish various types of habits.\n- support for adjusting habits and their order.\n- support to hide or show habits.\n- support for setting the start of each week.\n- dark/light appearance with free switching.\n- tracking of the various records of the habits.\n- simple and clear weekly, monthly and yearly clocking statistics.\n- widget feature, support displaying today/this week/this month punching status for each habit.\n- widget feature, supports displaying up to 7 habits' punching status for the week at the same time.\n- iCloud data auto-sync, seamless switching between multiple devices.\n\nIf you have any questions about using it, please contact shawn736_ios@163.com.",
